## AcceptIncomingCallBehavior enum

Determines the behavior when accepting an incoming call while there is currently another active call.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare enum AcceptIncomingCallBehavior 
```

## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  END\_CURRENT | <code>&quot;end-current&quot;</code> | Will end the currently active call before accepting the incoming call. |
|  HOLD\_CURRENT | <code>&quot;hold-current&quot;</code> | Will put the currently active call on hold before accepting the incoming call. |
